---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about__blob" data-parallax-blob aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="about__grid">
    <div class="about__image-wrap" data-reveal="left">
      <img src="/Yogurt/Hands4.jpg" alt="Woman holding smoothie." width="800" height="1000" class="about__image" />
    </div>
    <div class="about__content">
      <div class="about__quote-wrap" data-reveal="clip">
        <blockquote class="about__quote">Our Story</blockquote>
      </div>
      <p class="about__body" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="0.2">
        Meros was born from a simple belief — that what you consume should be as intentional as how you live. 
        Located in the heart of Yaletown, we craft every smoothie and yoghurt bowl from real ingredients, chosen with purpose. 
        No shortcuts. No compromise. Just food that's good for you, made beautifully.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 4;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: var(--space-24) var(--space-6);
    margin-top: -20px;
    box-shadow: 0 -10px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.13);
  }

  .about__blob {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -20% 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 45% at 85% 35%, rgba(201, 106, 74, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 35% 30% at 20% 70%, rgba(28, 46, 30, 0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
    will-change: transform;
  }

  .about__grid {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .about__image-wrap {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .about__content {
    padding: var(--space-8) 0;
  }

  .about__quote-wrap {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    border-top: var(--border-accent);
  }

  .about__quote {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }

  .about__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: var(--weight-light);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
